n呢D先叫打呀, 張生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20160814/large/1471115975_0c10.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20160814%2Flarge%2F1471115975_0c10.png&h=a2ed3900&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85adfb145bf9c8b528c04bf6406eb41ed5a25128","tid":523611,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:28:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/012405_d8b8bc65da179e45847804384791fd25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F012405_d8b8bc65da179e45847804384791fd25.jpg&h=c71c2520&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日下午時份，中大學生會收到一封寄給「中文大學學生會張秀賢」的匿名信，打開後內有一張有關我與初選對手在海麗邨調查上的剪報，上面貼有一條刀片，並用上紅色筆寫的一個「殺」字，以及塗去「張秀賢」名字。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊個係初選對手呀？<br />\n<br />\n報警未？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5078b36d216afadc8da9fa6e535ee29d3c8506","tid":523611,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"66dbd333e012f3cca60fdb7c31d15076c5bc2fd2","tid":523611,"uid":33864,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T18:54:32.000Z","msg":"五毛大軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:28:21.000Z","msg":"好多新a/c"},{"pid":"6abd850b20ccae45364fcf38e487f93674b085eb","tid":523611,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:29:40.000Z","msg":"何俊仁個頭先叫打<br />\n<br />\n保持距離 切勿跟車太貼"},{"pid":"3cdd62bd2a0d47aaa1130e77bb9a3410b09db9a4","tid":523611,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6abd850b20ccae45364fcf38e487f93674b085eb","tid":523611,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:29:40.000Z","msg":"何俊仁個頭先叫打<br />\n<br />\n保持距離 切勿跟車太貼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:31:25.000Z","msg":"呢種先叫打<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/640pix/20060821/Article_news/21la1p101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20060821%2FArticle_news%2F21la1p101.jpg&h=1c7d32e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢種就 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/lammm-01_z9Cqe_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Flammm-01_z9Cqe_1200x0.png&h=4ac4626b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6114714c2452fce79a376e884af2b16cb6e9d9b1","tid":523611,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"075d729892ffd9bd64f6feb206e6ad9b0c1f79de","tid":523611,"uid":48157,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T03:54:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:31:33.000Z","msg":"一單還一單, 海麗單野好似佢跟先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n.....張秀賢 對左膠好心出咗事<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">張秀賢 查圍標謎網，其實係佢同佢啲朋友做咗成半年嘅行動，本來同新東補選都無關，呢個人都係平日有鋪研究嘢嘅癮，你估好似班左膠見鏡頭就亂做研究。但 張秀賢 好心想交啲嘢俾姚松炎一啲意見，姚松炎周圍share，去到朱凱迪度，朱凱迪擺明係郭永健嘅真正幕後老闆，咪佢地根據啲人地嘅初步料當係人地嘅功勞囉。</span></strong>所以大家睇到， 張秀賢 幅謎網圖係實淨好多，工黨果幅係簡化得好緊要，因為 張秀賢 係自己研究，工黨班友係抄抄子。<br />\n<br />\n趙恩來唔出嚟9up，我都未必出嚟郁你班政界抄抄子，但趙恩來仲出嚟幫謎網關鍵嘅置佳管理講好說話，我就對你班工黨垃圾唔駛客氣。因為工黨直頭變咗維穩集團<br />\n<br />\n趙恩來-撚樣<br />\n趙恩來<br />\n趙恩來真係將新民黨果啲維穩作風都抄埋入嚟，當然有線電視大廈3002同3003係用同一入口果陣，根本係打通咗嘅單位，如果唔係同一辦公室，乜叫唔係同一辦公室？呢個係基本邏輯問題，但趙恩來為咗扶一個扶唔起嘅阿斗，就抄完人再9up，呢啲作風我之前遇過，除咗希師奶，就係熱普城班仆街，左膠幾時向熱普城學習佢地啲仆街嘢，好嘅唔學衰嘢學晒，香港政壇唔怪之得越嚟越墮落。<br />\n<br />\n仲要留意一樣，成個圍標謎網裡面，有工聯會份，所以支持工聯會本來好危險，加上海麗邨事件，工黨唔係應該呢個時候團結一致，槍頭對準工聯會班賊，依家竟然槍頭指向 張秀賢 ，呢班友嘅仆街度，真係同劉頴匡當年為咗隊冧范國威，叫人投土共一啲分別都無，所以鎅票黨喺關鍵時候，行為都係一樣，包括扮係支持打工仔女，實際上暗中替黃色工會護航。所以呢件事上面，趙恩來9up令我留番明日早上(香港時間)至恥笑葉劉淑儀喺布達佩斯啲膠嘢，優先煮重米向工黨開火。<br />\n<br />\n無論工黨定朱凱迪，依家香港人睇緊佢地係為香港人，定同民主黨班垃圾老人一樣為私怨而生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.martinoei.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/%E5%BC%B5%E7%A7%80%E8%B3%A2-768x542.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.martinoei.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2F%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E7%25A7%2580%25E8%25B3%25A2-768x542.jpg&h=41311225&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/16951/%E5%B7%A5%E9%BB%A8%E5%91%A2%E7%8F%AD%E6%8A%84%E6%8A%84%E5%AD%90%E6%8A%84%E5%AE%8C-%E5%BC%B5%E7%A7%80%E8%B3%A2-%E4%BB%B2%E8%A6%81%E5%90%AB%E8%A1%80%E5%99%B4%E4%BA%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F16951%2F%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E5%2591%25A2%25E7%258F%25AD%25E6%258A%2584%25E6%258A%2584%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%258A%2584%25E5%25AE%258C-%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E7%25A7%2580%25E8%25B3%25A2-%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%2590%25AB%25E8%25A1%2580%25E5%2599%25B4%25E4%25BA%25BA&d=u3M%2F3QMwHyjrno6sYRaUCMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=53ddd9eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/16951/%E5%B7%A5%E9%BB%A8%E5%91%A2%E7%8F%AD%E6%8A%84%E6%8A%84%E5%AD%90%E6%8A%84%E5%AE%8C-%E5%BC%B5%E7%A7%80%E8%B3%A2-%E4%BB%B2%E8%A6%81%E5%90%AB%E8%A1%80%E5%99%B4%E4%BA%BA</a>"},{"pid":"3f15e90a4688a0fbab0a9fe179c2b9ec17f24089","tid":523611,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6abd850b20ccae45364fcf38e487f93674b085eb","tid":523611,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:29:40.000Z","msg":"何俊仁個頭先叫打<br />\n<br />\n保持距離 切勿跟車太貼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:32:09.000Z","msg":"傳真社今次仲敢唔敢派記者睇CCTV? <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<